# Tracebud compact tab headers

- **Do not** duplicate `headerRowCompact`, `langPillCompact`, `headerTopRow`, or gradient header markup in screen files.
- Use **`CompactTabHeader`** from `apps/offline-app/tracebud-offline-app/components/layout/CompactTabHeader.tsx`.
- Shared metrics live in **`apps/offline-app/tracebud-offline-app/constants/compactTabHeader.ts`** (`HOME_HEADER_LOGO_PX`, `compactTabHeaderStyles`). Change layout in **one place** only.
- **Home**: pass **`left={<HomeHeaderBrandLeft subtitle={...} />}`** — logo + “Tracebud” + subtitle stay **left-aligned**; do **not** center the brand in an absolute overlay.
- **Settings / My Plots**: pass **`centerTitle={...}`** plus back button in **`left`** (see existing usages).
